snippet.title: Adobe Premiere Rush with Amber Torrealba - 2 of 3
snippet.description:
Join Amber Torrealba on Adobe Live as she edits a YouTube video for her channel, introducing you to Premiere Rush CC, Adobe’s brand new all-in-one video app! Today, Amber tweaks her transitions and adds sound effects.

Amber is a professional skimboarder who captures, edits and produces lifestyle content.

-----

►Check out Amber’s YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/ambertorrealba 
►Click HERE for part 3: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tv7U87loV1A

Recap: 2:20
Work Begins: 3:10
Reorienting video clips/rotating video: 16:45
Getting started with Rush: 22:45
Editing with vertical videos: 24:00
Clever transitions that mesh with your footage: 1:05:50
Editing videos to hold viewer attention: 1:09:15

► Click HERE to watch LIVE: http://bit.ly/AdobeLiveBe
